\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nu hon giua hai CDV Croatia va Nigeria\" title=\"N\u1ee5 h\u00f4n gi\u1eefa hai C\u0110V Croatia v\u00e0 Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/world-cup-2018-kiss4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">N\u1ee5 h\u00f4n gi\u1eefa hai C\u0110V Croatia v\u00e0 Nigeria</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nhung nu hon nong bong gop phan giup ngay hoi bong da lon nhat hanh tinh them lang man ben canh nhung cuoc tranh tai nay lua duoi san co.\" title=\"Nh\u1eefng n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh th\u00eam l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tranh t\u00e0i n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/world-cup-2018-kiss.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u1eefng n\u1ee5 h\u00f4n n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh th\u00eam l\u00e3ng m\u1ea1n b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng cu\u1ed9c tranh t\u00e0i n\u1ea3y l\u1eeda d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ecf.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"421","checkdouble":"189166"},{"date":"16:25 21/06","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n h\u1ee3p th\u1eddi cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-australia-va-nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-uc.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y tr\u00f4i qua, xu th\u1ebf th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee7a World Cup 2018 ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n r\u00f5. V\u00e0 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m ngo\u00e0i xu h\u01b0\u1edbng n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- <strong>Australia kh\u00f4ng thua </strong>(+1/2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0 ho\u1eb7c Australia th\u1eafng 1-0</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/link-xem-dan-mach-vs-australia-463-189157.html\">TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia 19h00 ng\u00e0y 21/6 (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia b\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018 l\u00fac...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u: </em>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia<br>\r\n<em>Th\u1eddi gian: </em>19h ng\u00e0y 21/6<br>\r\n<em>\u0110\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m: </em>Samara Arena (Samara)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>TLCA c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn: </em>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch -0.87*0:1/2*0.83 Australia<br>\r\n<em>TBT c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn:</em> Nhi\u1ec1u 0.92*2*-0.99 \u00cdt<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (\u00dac) v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia (\u00dac) v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n tr\u00ean Bongda24h h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-australia-va-nhan-dinh-dan-mach-vs-uc.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia 19h ng\u00e0y 21/6</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi (U 2)</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Peru v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Yussuf Poulsen. Nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 truy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kasper Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u01a1i cho Leicester \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 6 pha c\u1ee9u thua, \u0111a ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec1u ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSchmeichel t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u1edf tu\u1ed5i g\u1ea7n 32 m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 36 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Anh ch\u1ec9 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 2 n\u0103m sau khi c\u00f9ng Leicester v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi cha Peter Schmeichel v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"thu mon Schmeichel toa sang tai Dan Mach\" title=\"thu mon Schmeichel toa sang tai Dan Mach\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/thu-mon-Schmeichel-toa-sang-tai-Dan-Mach.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Schmeichel l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a c\u1ee7a \u0110T&nbsp;\u0110an M\u1ea1ch</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, Schmeichel \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Anh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Simon Kjaer l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec&rdquo; v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u00e1n s\u1ef1 trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1eadp trung \u1edf h\u1eadu ph\u01b0\u01a1ng gi\u00fap \u0110an M\u1ea1ch r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00ednh c\u1ea3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Peru, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 lo\u1ea1t giao h\u1eefu kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9ng. V\u00e0 v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 v\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 trong tay, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Age Hareide c\u00e0ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i thi tri\u1ec3n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia tin l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bong-da-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c-463-188649.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/ket-qua-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/bong-da-peru-vs-dan-mach-bang-c-463-188649.html\">Peru 0-1 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch (KT): D\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed3i, chi\u1ebfn binh Inca b\u1ea1i d\u01b0\u1edbi tay nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec</span><br>\r\n<span>Thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00e9p v\u1ebf h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 song Nh\u1eefng ch\u00fa l\u00ednh ch\u00ec l\u1ea1i s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ee9 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t: b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, Peru ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch m\u00ecnh khi b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 qu\u00e1...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn sang b\u00ean kia, Australia kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thua k\u00e9m \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 l\u1ef3 l\u1ee3m. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1 Ph\u00e1p t\u1edbi t\u1eadn ph\u00fat 80 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ecbu thua b\u1edfi b\u00e0n ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a Aziz Behich. C\u1ea7n bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u00e0 d\u00e0i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng qu\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Australia c\u0169ng c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y thua k\u00e9m v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n s\u1ebd h\u00f3a gi\u1ea3i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. M\u1ed9t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn gi\u1eb1ng co s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hai \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ea1o ra v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi khan hi\u1ebfm b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 chu\u1ed7i gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp<br>\r\n- 5 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n 4 b\u00e0n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ch\u1ecdn: </strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng (2 b\u00e0n tr\u1edf xu\u1ed1ng)<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Australia kh\u00f4ng thua (+1/2)</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n9 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o World Cup 2018, Australia ch\u1ec9 thua duy nh\u1ea5t 1 tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Na Uy. C\u00f2n l\u1ea1i 8 tr\u1eadn c\u1ea3 giao h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 5, h\u00f2a 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn thua 1-2 s\u00e1t n\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kho\u1ea3ng 5 ng\u00e0y, Australia c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p may. 2 b\u00e0n thua c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1edbi t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i. C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng t\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR m\u1edbi x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 penalty v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng qua v\u1ea1ch v\u00f4i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Australia thua dau Phap\" title=\"Australia thua dau Phap\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Australia-thua-dau-Phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Australia thua \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Phap</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c Australia thua k\u00e9m qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 l\u1ee5c l\u0103ng, nh\u01b0ng b\u00f9 l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c h\u1ebft gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. V\u00e0 tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 chu\u1ed9t t\u00fai h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Australia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua chi ti\u1ebft n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng 1-0 nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Poulsen ch\u1ec9 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm hoi m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a B\u1eafc \u00c2u t\u1ea1o ra. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1ecbu s\u1ee9c \u00e9p l\u1edbn t\u1eeb Peru v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 may m\u1eafn c\u00f9ng s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc Schmeichel m\u1edbi gi\u00fap h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAustralia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao nh\u01b0 Peru, nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ec5 ch\u01a1i. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea quan tr\u1ecdng:</strong><br>\r\n- Australia b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 8/10 tr\u1eadn v\u1eeba qua<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">- <strong>\u00cdt b\u00e0n th\u1eafng</strong> (kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 2 b\u00e0n)<br>\r\n- <strong>Australia kh\u00f4ng thua </strong>(+1/2)<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1: <strong>H\u00f2a 0-0 ho\u1eb7c Australia th\u1eafng 1-0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<h2>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t kh\u00e1c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Australia kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 2 qu\u1ea3 (+2)<br>\r\n- S\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a Australia kh\u00f4ng thua qu\u00e1 1 qu\u1ea3 (+3/4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 4 qu\u1ea3 (O 4)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 3 (U 3)<br>\r\n- T\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 1 (U 1)<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ea1nh H\u00f9ng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"420","checkdouble":"189168"},{"date":"16:54 21/06","title":"Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Juventus v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Juventus h\u1ecfi mua Bellerin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Hector Bellerin \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Arsenal. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7 nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/9/arsenal-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-juventus-voi-gia-45-trieu-bang.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Bellerin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. Theo The Sun, Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Hector Bellerin, h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Bellerin, h\u1ecd tin r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Arsenal nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Juventus c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Italia s\u1ebd c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Anh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ngay \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 n\u00e0y.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Bellerin</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-italia/juventus-mua-hau-ve-hector-bellerin-176-172922.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Bellerin </span>c\u1ee7a Arsenal, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bellerin\" title=\"Bellerin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/4/Hector-Bellerin-phat-bieu-ve-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Bellerin v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, HLV Unai Emery kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Bellerin l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i\u00a0sao 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDanh s\u00e1ch 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMU v\u00e0 Barca c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, song Arsenal s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb d\u00e0nh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"419","checkdouble":"189169"},{"date":"17:18 21/06","title":"\"MU c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/9/22/mk-dons-tha-thiet-moi-chao-ryan-giggs.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, M.U tr\u1eafng tay khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t danh hi\u1ec7u n\u00e0o. D\u1ea5u \u1ea5n duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng x\u1ebfp h\u1ea1ng Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Ryan-Giggs-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 4 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM.U \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred v\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Dalot. 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho v\u1eabn \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 130 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Giggs khuy\u00ean MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ryan Giggs ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"cuu tien ve Ryan Giggs\" title=\"cuu tien ve Ryan Giggs\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/12/22/Giggs-muon-tien-ve-Aaron-Ramsey-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ryan Giggs mu\u1ed1n MU mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho n\u00ean mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7. \u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 Rio Ferdinand trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 t\u1ed1t bi\u1ebft ch\u1ec9 huy h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7, M.U s\u1ebd h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n thua\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cM.U c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Carrick \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec7, M.U thi\u1ebfu \u0111i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 Mourinho c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid-172-189040.html\" target=\"_blank\">Giggs c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n MU mua Gareth Bale</span> c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, \u00f4ng tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiggs c\u0169ng tin r\u1eb1ng M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o Mourinho, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n gi\u1ecfi. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a M.U s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c M.U s\u1ebd c\u00f3 danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"418","checkdouble":"189170"},{"date":"17:30 21/06","title":"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup: Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/peru-tai-xuat-an-tuong-o-world-cup-khi-that-bai-chi-nam-lai-tren-bang-ty-so.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u1ec7t k\u00ea ra nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 v\u00f4 t\u01b0 c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 trung l\u1eadp cho k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 n\u00e0y, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Peru s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u danh s\u00e1ch c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi v\u00e0i ba con ng\u1ef1a \u00f4 kh\u00e1c.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 36 n\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eafp n\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i danh ph\u1eadn t\u00e2n binh nh\u01b0 Iceland hay Panama, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Peru \u1edf l\u1ec5 h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Nga n\u00e0y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u1edbi. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb Espana 1982 th\u00ec \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i World Cup sau 36 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/172102-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau 36 n\u0103m v\u1eafng b\u00f3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, Los Incas quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i l\u00e2u h\u01a1n giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u1edf T\u00e2y Ban Nha x\u01b0a kia. HLV Ricardo Gareca, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 60 tu\u1ed5i t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Argentina v\u00e0 s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u1ea1nh b\u00ean Diego Maradona, d\u1ef1ng x\u00e2y n\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 kh\u00f4ng ai cao n\u1ed5i 1m85 v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac v\u1edbi tham v\u1ecdng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua nh\u1eefng Australia hay \u0110an M\u1ea1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/cdv-peru-tai-world-cup-2018-ngoi-xe-lan-ban-xe-hoi-de-theo-chan-doi-tuyen-465-189165.html\" target=\"_blank\">C\u00e1c C\u0110V Peru t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018</span> ng\u00fat ng\u00e0n ni\u1ec1m tin kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m g\u00ec HLV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, h\u00e3y c\u1ee9 nh\u00ecn l\u1ec5 c\u1eed h\u00e0nh qu\u1ed1c ca h\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eam nghi\u1ec7m. 43 ngh\u00ecn v\u00e9 m\u00e1y bay sang Nga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf qu\u00ea nh\u00e0, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 con s\u1ed1 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 theo ch\u00e2n \u0110TQG d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea5p \u0111\u00f4i. M\u00e0n t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau 36 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ee7 l\u1edbn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ee7 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00f3 h\u1eadu.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110inh m\u1ec7nh huy\u1ec1n di\u1ec7u g\u1ecdi t\u00ean</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ni\u1ec1m tin b\u1ea5t di\u1ec7t \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft ngu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb phong c\u00e1ch b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eadn hi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareca, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed3i \u0111\u1eafp b\u1edfi chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i huy\u1ec1n di\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. \u0110ong \u0111\u1ebfm v\u1eadn may \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Peru \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018, ai \u0111\u00f3 theo ch\u1ee7 ngh\u0129a duy t\u00e2m c\u0169ng s\u1ebd qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5ng t\u1ed1i cao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Inca.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Peru-tai-xuat-an-tuong-o-World-Cup-Khi-that-bai-chi-nam-lai-tren-bang-ty-so-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i khu v\u1ef1c Nam M\u1ef9 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tranh cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn play-off li\u00ean l\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ecba v\u1edbi Chile kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh h\u01a1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eefa. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eb7ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 tr\u00ean tr\u1eddi r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng sau khi nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1edbi Bolivia b\u1ecb h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf do \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ngo\u1ea1i qu\u1ed1c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 2 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Chile (h\u00f2a Bolivia) nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ebfn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m cho Peru (thua Bolivia).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1ee5 b\u00ea b\u1ed1i Bolivia b\u1ecb phanh phui, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa Chile v\u00e0 Peru \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ng\u1eafn xu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. Thi\u1ec7t th\u00f2i \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat nh\u01b0ng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf v\u00e0 quy\u1ec1n t\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Chile, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng m\u1ecdi b\u1ea5t tr\u1eafc.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, Chile th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 0-3 \u1edf Brazil v\u00e0 k\u00e9o t\u1ee5t hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi Peru, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a v\u1edbi Colombia.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u1ecdi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ec7nh khi t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 World Cup 2018 v\u1eabn n\u1eb1m ch\u1eafc trong tay Chile cho \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Brazil ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 ba \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 3500km \u1edf b\u1edd bi\u1ec3n b\u00ean kia Nam M\u1ef9, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n David Ospina l\u00f3ng ng\u00f3ng ph\u1ea3n l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 t\u1eeb pha \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t gi\u00e1n ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Paolo Guerrero, trao l\u1ea1i 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0ng r\u00f2ng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Peru v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t s\u1ee9 m\u1ec7nh tr\u01b0\u1edbc New Zealand.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Peru-tai-xuat-an-tuong-o-World-Cup-Khi-that-bai-chi-nam-lai-tren-bang-ty-so-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng gi\u1ecdt n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Christian Cueva</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u1eddi ch\u00e0o World Cup k\u00e9m may v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Peru t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng h\u1ebft \u201cqu\u1ef9 may m\u1eafn\u201d c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn Nga \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i ngay \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111en h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 \u201cl\u00ednh ch\u00ec\u201d \u0110an M\u1ea1ch. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Los Incas v\u1edbi th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 phong c\u00e1ch t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 thanh tho\u00e1t, r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 phi\u00eau l\u01b0u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00f4n ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7t ng\u00e3 t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn c\u1ee7a n\u00f3, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Mordovia \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup c\u1ee7a Peru v\u1eabn kh\u00edch l\u1ec7 ni\u1ec1m hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch v\u1edbi k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u00f3 h\u1eadu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd, Peru c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft t\u1ef1 tr\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i b\u1ecb phung ph\u00ed.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-peru-22h00-ngay-216-them-mot-doi-roi-cuoc-choi-462-189134.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-peru-22h00-ngay-216-them-mot-doi-roi-cuoc-choi.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-phap-vs-peru-22h00-ngay-216-them-mot-doi-roi-cuoc-choi-462-189134.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1p vs Peru (22h00 ng\u00e0y 21/6): Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i?</span><br>\r\nLi\u1ec7u Peru c\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n ti\u1ebfp theo ph\u1ea3i s\u1eafp s\u1eb5n vali tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ec9 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018?</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi bao nhi\u00eau v\u1edbi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang v\u1ec1 qu\u1ea3 penalty qu\u00fd gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau khi Christian Cueva v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a n\u00f3 th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i x\u00fac c\u1ea3m b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 khi k\u1ebft th\u00fac hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Peru c\u00e0ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft keo s\u01a1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi v\u1ed7 v\u1ec1 an \u1ee7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00c2u lo nghi ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, khi Cueva kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u1ed7i ni\u1ec1m ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u00e0 day d\u1ee9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n trong 45 ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Anh c\u00f9ng Andre Carrillo b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 hai ng\u00f2i n\u1ed5 nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Peru, gieo r\u1eafc m\u1ed1i h\u1ecda kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 B\u1eafc \u00c2u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Peru t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/172111-4.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Peru t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng: Khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00e2u d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00ec ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00f3. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-vat/paolo-guerrero-thu-linh-so-1-cua-nhung-chien-binh-inca-389-189167.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh Paulo Guerrero</span> ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai v\u1edbi c\u00fa gi\u1eadt g\u00f3t bi\u1ec3u th\u1ecb cho tr\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Peru, nh\u01b0ng vi\u1ec7c tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc trong gang t\u1ea5c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecdng v\u1eadn \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hi\u1ec3n nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, quy lu\u1eadt mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf \u0111\u00e3 linh \u1ee9ng v\u00e0o Peru khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 c\u00e1i gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t. \u0110\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00fang m\u1ed9t gi\u1edd thi \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng Christian Eriksen \u0111\u1ea1o di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1ee3t ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc s\u1ea3o trong th\u1ebf 3v3, l\u00ean b\u00f3ng th\u1ea7n t\u1ed1c r\u1ed3i ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t cho Yussuf Poulsen tung nh\u00e1t dao k\u1ebft li\u1ec5u \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/paolo-guerrero-thu-linh-so-1-cua-nhung-chien-binh-inca-389-189167.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/paolo-guerrero-thu-linh-so-1-cua-nhung-chien-binh-inca.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-vat/paolo-guerrero-thu-linh-so-1-cua-nhung-chien-binh-inca-389-189167.html\">Paolo Guerrero: Th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh Inca</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u201cGuerrero\u201d trong ti\u1ebfng T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 \u201cchi\u1ebfn binh\u201d. \u1ede tu\u1ed5i 34, Paolo Guerrero kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng \u201cchi\u1ebfn binh Inca\u201d t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Peru cay \u0111\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng, qu\u1eadt kh\u1edfi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c \u00e9p kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng v\u00e0 theo th\u1eddi gian, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareca d\u1ea7n nh\u1eadn ra h\u00f4m nay kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 ri\u00eang c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft n\u00ean nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp theo sau Euro 1992. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Peru m\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i luy\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfc cho m\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup. D\u00f9 sao, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 n\u1eb1m l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean b\u1ea3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong> <o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"417","checkdouble":"189172"},{"date":"17:37 21/06","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Croatia: H\u00e3y c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi Leo Messi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/11/9/truoc-tran-gap-croatia-hay-cong-bang-voi-leo-messi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n v\u1edbi g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng, El Pulga nh\u01b0 n\u1eafm tr\u00ean vai v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c, v\u00e0 anh s\u00fat tr\u00fang tay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch? H\u1eb3n r\u1ed3i, nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 bao gi\u1edd ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta hi\u1ec3u Messi c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng?\r\n</h2><h2>Messi v\u00e0 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 si\u00eau ph\u00e0m, kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf cao ng\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng vi\u1ec7c si\u00eau \u0111\u1eb3ng, nh\u01b0 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi &ndash; gi\u1ed1ng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Diego Maradona.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Argentina li\u00ean t\u1ee5c h\u00e1t vang t\u00ean Messi. &ldquo;V\u1edbi b\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a anh \u1ea5y, ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Ngay trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Messi khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Iceland. H\u01a1n n\u1eefa, l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n x\u1ecbt pen.<br>\r\n</strong> <br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Croatia Messi c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Croatia Messi c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/16/Truoc-tran-gap-Croatia-Messi-can-su-cong-bang-tai-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 1986, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Leo Messi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ra \u0111\u1eddi, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Argentina \u0111\u00e3 ca ng\u1ee3i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n tay kh\u00e1c &ndash; &ldquo;B\u00e0n tay c\u1ee7a Ch\u00faa&rdquo; \u0111em v\u1ec1 World Cup, Diego Maradona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung h\u00f4 l\u00e0m th\u00e1nh s\u1ed1ng. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n Messi c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ecf qua nh\u1eefng so s\u00e1nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng &ndash; v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Maradona. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean quay ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i pha ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng tay n\u00f3i tr\u00ean, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn &ldquo;C\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng&rdquo; kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n m\u1eebng, khi FIFA World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a&hellip; VAR.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, Maradona v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1986 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c HLV v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 truy c\u1eadp v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a anh. Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n theo d\u00f5i Maradona thi \u0111\u1ea5u, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u00e0 t\u00e1c nghi\u1ec7p nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Barca, sau n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Napoli. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd, c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i cho ph\u00e9p ch\u00fang ta t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 th\u00f3i quen ghi s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Leo Messi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3&hellip; Hannes Thor Halldorsson (th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Iceland).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, t\u1ea1i Argentina l\u00fac n\u00e0y, Leo Messi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Nh\u00ecn sang Barcelona, anh c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 cho anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Argentina gay that vong tran tre ngay ra quan truoc Iceland\" title=\"Argentina g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00e0n tr\u1ec1 ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Nhan-dinh-Argentina-vs-Croatia-(01h00-ngay-226)-Chua-cung-bat-luc-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u01b0ng Argentina c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c n\u00e0o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nTr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 th\u1ef1c t\u1ea1i, Argentina \u0111ang b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 sau khi b\u1ecb Iceland c\u1ea7m ch\u00e2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng Croatia, v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 xua tan m\u00e2y m\u00f9. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi v\u1ecb th\u1ebf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Albicelestes ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n kh\u00f3 nh\u1eb1n nh\u01b0 Croatia, Messi c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u00ecn xem \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ra sao? <em><strong>&ldquo;Di Maria kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t pha qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u00f2n 2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 g\u00ec cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y&rdquo;</strong></em> &ndash; c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hernan Crespo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 linh ho\u1ea1t, khi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Messi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u1eddng. Aguero \u0111\u00f3i b\u00f3ng, trong khi Higuain c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m g\u00ec v\u1edbi 5 ph\u00fat \u00edt \u1ecfi g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. B\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi, h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 bao, khi th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Caballero li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong kh\u00e2u ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, h\u00f2a Iceland l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, <strong>Messi v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o, tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi Argentina\" title=\"Messi Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/9/argentina-va-nhung-bai-toan-cho-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi c\u1ea7n c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Argentina gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV Sampaoli bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00f9i, v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng Argentina c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng n\u00e9t t\u00edch c\u1ef1c m\u1edbi. S\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u00e1nh bi\u00ean. H\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i, khi Aguero r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u ngay c\u1ea1nh m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadt may, Argentina v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Banega, Dybala v\u00e0 Higuain ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 nu\u1ed1t l\u1ea5y to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Leo Messi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, anh v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i xung quanh c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u00f3i quen b\u1eaft ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y &ldquo;g\u00e1nh team&rdquo;. Ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u00f3, Argentina m\u1edbi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Croatia, v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, hay xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/me-messi-con-trai-toi-khoc-nhieu-lan-trong-mau-ao-dtqg-argentina-421-189155.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/me-messi-con-trai-toi-khoc-nhieu-lan-trong-mau-ao-dtqg-argentina.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/me-messi-con-trai-toi-khoc-nhieu-lan-trong-mau-ao-dtqg-argentina-421-189155.html\">M\u1eb9 Messi: Con trai t\u00f4i kh\u00f3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG Argentina</span><br>\r\nB\u00e0 Celia Cuccittini chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m bu\u1ed3n m\u00e0 con trai Lionel Messi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-vs-croatia-01h00-ngay-226-chua-cung-bat-luc-421-189128.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/argentina-vs-croatia-01h00-ngay-226-chua-cung-bat-luc.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-vs-croatia-01h00-ngay-226-chua-cung-bat-luc-421-189128.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia (01h00 ng\u00e0y 22/6): Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea5ng c\u1ee9u th\u1ebf, xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t m\u1ecdi th\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i &ndash; r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng m\u1ef9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh cho Leo Messi, nh\u01b0ng theo nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Argentina vs Croatia, \u0111\u00e2y qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i to\u00e1n...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sampaoli-chua-biet-sap-xep-nhan-su-the-nao-truoc-croatia-421-189129.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/27/sampaoli-chua-biet-sap-xep-nhan-su-the-nao-truoc-croatia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sampaoli-chua-biet-sap-xep-nhan-su-the-nao-truoc-croatia-421-189129.html\">Sampaoli ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1eafp x\u1ebfp nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ed1 ph\u1eadn c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, HLV Argentina ch\u01b0a x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Croatia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"416","checkdouble":"189173"},{"date":"09:36 21/06","title":"Diego Costa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iran","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/diego-costa-khang-dinh-khong-choi-xau-thu-mon-iran.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n c\u1ee7a \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Diego Costa th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 th\u1eafng may nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"TBN Costa tranh bong voi Iran\" title=\"TBN Costa tranh bong voi Iran\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/HLV-Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Iran</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Iran \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 t\u1eed th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Trong su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat La Roja \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Iran. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi hi\u1ec7p 2, ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha m\u1edbi may m\u1eafn c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khi c\u00fa ph\u00e1 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Iran l\u1ea1i v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh \u0111\u1eadp ch\u00e2n Diego Costa v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0, Costa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Anh n\u00f3i: &ldquo;Th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn khi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ed1t hi\u1ec7p 1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Iran \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho TBN b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng pha n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n li\u00ean t\u1ee5c d\u00f9 nh\u1eefng pha va ch\u1ea1m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn th\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1eddi kh\u1eafc th\u00edch h\u1ee3p&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng cho Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 \u00fd ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Iran Alireza Beiranvand. &quot;V\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Beiranvand, t\u00f4i ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng v\u00ec bi\u1ebft xung quanh m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u m\u00e1y quay. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 Beiranvand ph\u1ea3i t\u1ecf ra \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn nh\u01b0 v\u1eady&quot;, Costa qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i tinh qu\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Costa di\u1ec5n ra trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1 tuy nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 tr\u1eebng ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool Jamie Redknapp&nbsp;th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a Costa l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/tong-hop-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bang-b-world-cup-2018-461-189115.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha (B\u1ea3ng B World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Hierro \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t Iran kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n h\u01a1n d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1edd v\u00e0o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Diego Costa, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-bo-tot-run-ray-gianh-3-diem-421-189120.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha: &ldquo;B\u00f2 t\u00f3t&rdquo; run r\u1ea9y gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</span><br>\r\nM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n Iran song T\u00e2y Ban Nha ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1ed1i thi\u1ec3u. Tr\u1eadn Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha b\u1ea3ng B World Cup...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-421-189119.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/TBN-an-mung-tran-thang-Iran-1-0.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-dau-iran-01-tay-ban-nha-421-189119.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Iran 0-1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng B VCK World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/HLV-Carlos-Queiroz-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Iran-vs-TBN-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-dieu-rut-ra-sau-du-am-iran-vs-tay-ban-nha-421-189116.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n 1-0 c\u1ee7a TBN tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran</span><br>\r\nD\u01b0 \u00e2m Iran vs T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u1ed1n kh\u00f3 t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n. TBN ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn c\u1ee7a Diego Costa m\u1edbi v\u01b0\u1ee3t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"415","checkdouble":"189135"},{"date":"09:51 21/06","title":"U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/u19-viet-nam-tiep-tuc-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-trung-quoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>G\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1eafng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn n\u1eefa v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm.</h2><h2>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c. T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/DT-U19-Viet-Nam-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-Trung-Quoc-hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n gi\u00f2n gi\u00e3 khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Meizhou v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 6-0. V\u00e0 \u1edf l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam nhanh ch\u00f3ng l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, h\u1ecd th\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp Meizhou 5-0. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1eefa v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24/6 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 26/6. \u0110\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, ch\u1ed1t danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 14/7 t\u1ea1i Jakarta (Indonesia). \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, Th\u00e1i Lan, Singapore, L\u00e0o, Philippines. B\u1ea3ng B c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Malaysia, Myanmar, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, Campuchia v\u00e0 Brunei.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a khu v\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, Th\u00e1i Lan, Indonesia v\u00e0 Malaysia chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho VCK U19 Ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, c\u0169ng s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Indonesia v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/DT-U19-Viet-Nam-co-chien-thang-dam-tai-Trung-Quoc-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam-168-186505.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/indonesia-goi-hang-khung-tu-chau-au-ve-dau-u19-viet-nam-168-186505.html\">Indonesia g\u1ecdi h\u00e0ng kh\u1ee7ng t\u1eeb ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea5u U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</span><br>\r\n\u0110T U19 Indonesia m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Ba Lan, &ldquo;s\u00e1t th\u1ee7&rdquo; Egy Maulana \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"414","checkdouble":"189137"},{"date":"10:56 21/06","title":"Carvajal l\u00ean \u00e1n chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Iran","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/21/carvajal-len-an-chien-thuat-tieu-cuc-cua-iran.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>b